USER: "Hey Alexa, what can i eat for dinner?"

Alexa: "What kind of dinner do you want to have?"

User: "A romantic dinner for two."

Alexa: "Do you want to have a vegetarian dinner?"

User: "No."

Alexa: "I can propose a salmon filet with rice."

User: "That's good for me. What wine can you propose to have with this dinner?"

Alexa: "I can propose a mosel-riessling from 2016."

User: "I'd like a bottle of that as well."

Alexa: "Do you want to have anything else with that?"

User: "No, that's it."

Alexa: "Ok, we'll prepare everything for you and you can pick it up at you local Lidl store."

